---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Application Received | For Psychologists | Sydney Anxiety Psychology"
  description="Thank you for applying to list your practice on the Sydney Anxiety Psychology directory. We will be in touch within 2 business days."
>
  <div class="main-content">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 560px; text-align: center; padding-top: 3rem;">

      <div style="width: 64px; height: 64px; background: var(--color-accent-soft); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;">
        <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
      </div>

      <h1 style="font-size: 1.85rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Application received</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Thank you for applying to list your practice on the Sydney Anxiety Psychology directory. We will review your application and be in touch within 2 business days.</p>

      <div class="info-box" style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <p><strong>What happens next:</strong> We verify your AHPRA registration, review your details, and create or enrich your profile. Once your listing is live, we will email you with the link and instructions for how enquiries will reach you. If we have questions about your application, we will contact you at the email address you provided.</p>
      </div>

      <a href="/" class="btn btn--secondary">
        Back to the directory
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
